### Registry Basics - Test Endpoints

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### 1. Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### 2. Send Email
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "user@example.com",
  "subject": "Test Email from Registry",
  "body": "This email was sent using a service from the registry!"
}

### 3. Send Email - Validation Error (invalid email)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/email/send
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "to": "invalid-email",
  "subject": "Test",
  "body": "Test"
}

### 4. Increment Counter
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/counter/increment

### 5. Increment Counter Again (should show 102)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/counter/increment

### 6. Get Counter Value
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/counter/value

### 7. Test Multiple Increments
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/counter/increment
